   Mission, Vision, and Values
   On behalf of the Employment Development Department (EDD), I welcome you
   to explore our Web site. We are one of the largest state
   departments--with nearly 10,000 employees and more than 400 service
   locations. For more than 60 years, we have connected millions of job
   seekers and employers in an effort to build the economy of this Golden
   State.
   Our Web site is your link to:
     * An online job and résumé bank (CalJOBS), which boasts thousands of
       job openings and the largest pool of candidates in the state,
     * Labor market tools designed to help you make educated decisions,
     * Information on filing an Unemployment Insurance or Disability
       Insurance claim,
     * The latest employment tax information and forms, and
     * A wide array of employment and training services, and more!

   I hope you find our site helpful and informative.
   Michael S. Bernick
   EDD Director
